contentrichtext.text: '''Godric''' may refer to: *[[Godric of Finchale]], an Anglo-Saxon saint *[[Godric the Sheriff]], an 11th-century sheriff of Buckinghamshire and Berkshire *[[Characters of True Blood#Godric|Godric]], a fictional character in the television series ''True Blood'' based on the Southern Vampire Chronicles by Charlaine Harris. *[[Godric of Winchcombe]], a medieval abbot of [[Winchcombe Abbey]] *[[Godric (novel)|''Godric'' (novel)]], a Pulitzer-nominated book by Frederick Buechner *[[Hogwarts staff#Godric Gryffindor|Godric Gryffindor]], a fictional character in the ''Harry Potter'' universe **[[Places in Harry Potter#Godric's Hollow|Godric's Hollow]], a fictional place in the ''Harry Potter'' universe {{disambig}}
